Package com.facebook.buck.core.exceptions

Class DependencyStack

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.core.exceptions.DependencyStack
  • public final class DependencyStack
extends Object
    Stack-trace for providing better diagnostics when working with dependency graph.

    This type must not be used for anything except for providing error diagnostics.
